node.text:
Repost from @theshaderoomteens
•
#TSRTPositiveImages: 
@FashionNovaCares and #TheShadeRoom @NoIGAngelica donate $100K to @Peace4Kids to support their ROCMove initiative. @ROCMove is a multigenerational initiative led predominantly by women and girls with lived experience in foster care. It's designed to uplift media and interactive training to highlight stories of power, transformation and resilience, evolving our country’s negative perception of foster care. For 22 years Peace4Kids has been fueled by the idea that youth in foster care deserve equitable opportunities to create community and connect with people who authentically care for them. Peace4Kids honors the intergenerational voices of foster care and provides the tools to navigate past trauma, embrace the future and thrive.  #NationalFosterCareMonth #FashionNovaCares

node.title: Why The Foster Care System Needs Us
